Good service and fine food, price is acceptable, live band singer , prefect place for gathering and dine in.

It is a restaurant run by senior people.  They serve vegetarian buffet breakfast in the morning.  They have set lunch menu.  There is one thing special is that they serve semi-buffet dinner with live band singing golden songs every night from 7 to 9 pm.  The food is good and the atmosphere is nice.
Value for money.  Service was good

result.name: Gingko Moment

reviews.text: a very entertaining restaurant  and a yummy foods too. you must visit it. highly recommended

A hidden gem in the city for vegetarian and wine lovers! They employ seniors as waiters and provide buffets for fellow vegetarians! 
The restaurant is clean and neat, well indoor design and cozy environment, wooden shelves make it more natural. Plenty choices of food in the morning buffet, waiters greeting and service are home-welcoming and heartwarming. 
Self serving fry eggs are cute. Coffee, tea and soy milk provided, so as congee, steam buns, fried noodles and baked beans etc.
A nice place to visit if you want a healthy meal.

The food is only so so but it is one of the rare places in the neighborhood which you don't have to queue up thus nobody queueing up after you, so one could linger over conversation with friends and family on a Sunday. Service is pretty good too, and most importantly it is a social enterprise so you may spend on a good cause, not bad right?
This is a hidden gem! The food was good and the company and service were excellent. Can’t wait to return when visiting again.

Restaurant is really cute with a Cantonese fusion menu offering Asian and western dishes.  I got the vegetable curry which was favorable with a tiny bit of kick and full of veggies. Service is typical HK but for a restaurant that purposely hires elderly staff, not that bad!

銀杏時光的服務員大多是銀髮一族，服務態度很好很親切，可閒話家常，食品質素也不錯。晚餐一般都是選擇半自助餐形式，有菜湯及自助生果/薯仔沙律及一杯飲品。餐廳有現埸樂隊獻唱懷舊中西歌曲，水準一般啦！大致而言，如果要求不太高的話，不失為一間可以一試的餐廳。

result.name: 銀杏館 銀杏時光

reviews.text: 喜歡聽歌，吃飯好地方，尤其是我60年後，老歌啱聽

銀杏館是社會企業，專門顧用年長人仕重投社會工作。
它在荔枝角分店結速之後遷置鰂魚涌基利路，鰂魚涌社區會堂對面。開業至現在漸漸上軌道！開業初時光顧過，發覺價錢和食物水準不平衡。但上週星期四晚再光顧時就發覺食物水準提高好多，絕對物有所值！😋😋😋😋😋
食物水準穩定，週日半自助午餐自助沙律吧選擇較少，馳名自助空氣棉花糖機數月前損壞後未再出現，稍為失色
品質尚可，有懷舊feel，可以！
食物品質不錯, 服務員有禮, 最重要是支持長者就業社企, 值得支持
